title: gccgo: doesn't recognize Linux s390x (IBM) 64-bit ar archive
body:
by **gongsugongsu**: 
gccgo version 4.8

When importing ar archive on Linux s390x, gccgo complains:

libyagnats.a: bad extended name index at 8

This is likely because the archive has a /SYM64/ header which gccgo doesn't recognize.
